# GradebookShell

**GradebookShell** is a Java-based command-line application for managing class gradebooks. It supports instructors in creating classes, managing categories, assignments, and students, and recording grades, all backed by an SQLite database.

---

## ðŸ’¾ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/GradebookShell.git
cd GradebookShell
```
### 2. Compile the Program
```bash
javac -cp ".;sqlite-jdbc-3.49.1.0.jar" GradebookShell.java
```
### 3. Run the Program
```bash
java -cp ".;sqlite-jdbc-3.49.1.0.jar" GradebookShell gradebook.db
```